705741f-a.title: Brooklyn: Milton Street - Franklin Street
705741f-a.text:
Milton Street, east from Franklin Street to Manhattan Ave., showing
on the left, in the background, the St. John's Lutheran Church, at No. 155;
in the extreme background, the St. Anthony of Padua R.C. Church, at No. 870
Manhattan Ave.
April 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
N.n. ~235g
